   "t": 13719,
   "s": "err",
   "x": "## Spec"
  },
  {
   "t": 13719,
   "s": "err",
   "x": "- Input: array of plain objects. Output: a GitHub-flavored markdown table string."
  },
  {
   "t": 13719,
   "s": "err",
   "x": "- Columns: the union of all keys, in first-seen order (scanning rows in order, keys in object order)."
  },
  {
   "t": 13719,
   "s": "err",
   "x": "- Missing values render as empty string. Non-string values via `String(value)`."
  },
  {
   "t": 13719,
   "s": "err",
   "x": "- Every cell is left-aligned and padded with spaces so all rows of a column share the same width. Column width = max length of the header and every value in that column (minimum 3)."
  },
  {
   "t": 13719,
   "s": "err",
   "x": "- Format per row: `| cell | cell |` (single space inside each pipe). Separator row uses dashes filling the full column width."
  },
  {
   "t": 13719,
   "s": "err",
   "x": "- Rows joined with `\\n`, no trailing newline. Empty input array -> empty string."
  },
  {
